{"tid":1728424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"提議：全民做善事（例如 全民捐血日）","createTime":"2019-11-17T01:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T01:11:35.000Z","uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f39872f62420b45d6b478780df7750528ec93f9","tid":1728424,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"為咗展現高質民意反極權，而遊行/集會/以武制暴 只係展現民意其中抗爭方式<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有人話抗爭要融入生活，呢類運動正好食正個理念</span><br />\n<br />\n與其我地有咁多人 不如一齊做善事 比全世界人知道 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我們不是暴徒，而係充滿愛心，愛香港既香港人」</span></span><br />\n因此我有一個建議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一齊去做有意義 亦對社會有實質貢獻工作</span></span><br />\n例如 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民捐血日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n之前成日聽到血庫唔夠血 要 呼籲捐血<br />\n不如就一齊去啦，<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為多區都有捐血站，個行為等於開花</span>，不過係善事開花，相信能夠<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">正面地展現抗爭可愛一面</span>[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n一日捐唔晒 就下星期再捐，捐到血庫爆為止！<br />\n<br />\nDressing Code: All Black<br />\n<br />\n唯一係安全考慮，因為要<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">登記ID先可以捐血，所以全日係以和理非姿態進行</span></span>，以免比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得可以請幫推同埋研究文宣同set日程，sorry因為我唔識搞文宣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考各區捐血站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticle.asp%3Fbid%3D85%26MenuID%3D5%23.Xc9TfyV-WaM&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=ada79bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMk6ZiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMk6ZiB.jpg&h=da7845c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞個暗黑全民日笑下：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民捐精日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs. 呢隻跳舞連登豬真係幾得意"},{"pid":"4a96a6317d2121d5e69c9e23f8375915bf7eaacd","tid":1728424,"uid":1048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rD34TKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrD34TKU.png&h=54ecaa33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一繼續黎明行動</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7f585c2d00231965466d27b6003dec0dbfefb912","tid":1728424,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"002c161397d4fd936dabef0754c39440284178ae","tid":1728424,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:10:00.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"7a282a404f3451ec20321010e16b12f514f18fb5","tid":1728424,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:10:11.000Z","msg":